N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6655.10 - Restriction on delegation

State Regulations

Except for OAA funds covered by transportation agreements
under section
6654.14
of this Title, the office
and area agencies may not delegate to another agency the authority to award or
administer OAA, CSE or EISEP funds. Notes
